---
---
<div class="specs-band">
    <div class="container specs-band-inner">
        <div class="spec-item">
            <i class="ph ph-gear"></i>
            <div><span>CARCAZAS</span><strong>SAE 6 &ndash; 00</strong></div>
        </div>
        <div class="spec-divider"></div>
        <div class="spec-item">
            <i class="ph ph-disc"></i>
            <div><span>DISCOS DE FRICCI&Oacute;N</span><strong>1, 2 Y 3</strong></div>
        </div>
        <div class="spec-divider"></div>
        <div class="spec-item">
            <i class="ph ph-ruler"></i>
            <div><span>DI&Aacute;METRO</span><strong>&Oslash;165 &ndash; 457 mm</strong></div>
        </div>
        <div class="spec-divider"></div>
        <div class="spec-item">
            <i class="ph ph-wrench"></i>
            <div><span>TORQUE</span><strong>HASTA 12.000 Nm</strong></div>
        </div>
        <div class="spec-divider mobile-hidden"></div>
        <div class="spec-item mobile-hidden">
            <i class="ph ph-shield-check"></i>
            <div><span>CONSTRUCCI&Oacute;N</span><strong>INDUSTRIAL PESADA</strong></div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<section class="selection-section" id="especificaciones">
    <div class="container selection-inner">
        <div class="selection-blueprint" data-reveal>
            <img src="/plano.png" alt="Plano técnico" class="blueprint-img">
        </div>

        <div class="selection-content">
            <div class="section-kicker light" data-reveal>Ingenier&iacute;a aplicada</div>
            <h2 class="selection-title" data-reveal style="--i: 1">Par&aacute;metros de selecci&oacute;n t&eacute;cnica</h2>
            <p class="selection-copy" data-reveal style="--i: 2">Cada aplicaci&oacute;n exige una evaluaci&oacute;n de ingenier&iacute;a para definir la toma de fuerza correcta. Se eval&uacute;an los siguientes par&aacute;metros:</p>

            <div class="selection-list" data-reveal style="--i: 3">
                <div><strong>01</strong><span>Motor y potencia<br>(HP / CV)</span></div>
                <div><strong>02</strong><span>RPM de trabajo<br>(VAC / MAX)</span></div>
                <div><strong>03</strong><span>Torque nominal<br>requerido</span></div>
                <div><strong>04</strong><span>Tipo de equipo<br>accionado</span></div>
                <div><strong>05</strong><span>Factor de carga<br>de arranque</span></div>
                <div><strong>06</strong><span>Frecuencia de<br>acoplamiento</span></div>
                <div><strong>07</strong><span>Sistema de<br>accionamiento</span></div>
                <div><strong>08</strong><span>Dimensiones<br>carcaza SAE</span></div>
                <div><strong>09</strong><span>P&eacute;rdidas del<br>eje de salida</span></div>
                <div><strong>10</strong><span>Temperatura /<br>ambiente</span></div>
            </div>

            <a href="#contacto" class="btn btn-gold selection-cta" data-reveal style="--i: 4"><i class="ph ph-paper-plane-tilt"></i> Enviar datos t&eacute;cnicos a ingenier&iacute;a</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
